  "description": "A dramatic image captures a total lunar eclipse, often called a blood moon, against a star-speckled black sky. The moon appears as a deep reddish-orange orb, its surface textured with subtle variations in shading. Tiny, distant stars are scattered throughout the darkness, adding to the cosmic atmosphere. The eclipse is the clear focal point, dominating the scene with its unusual coloration and imposing size. It evokes a sense of wonder and the vastness of space.",
